      {"op": "add_text", "slide_index": 9, "text": "Native language UX\nBahasa, Vietnamese, Thai interfaces — not translated, but built natively with local UX conventions and input methods.\n\nLocal payment integration\nDirect integration with GoPay, MoMo, PromptPay, and 20+ local payment methods. Settlement in local currencies.\n\nRegional data residency\nIn-country data centers in Jakarta, Ho Chi Minh City, and Bangkok for compliance with local data sovereignty laws.", "left": 0.9, "top": 2.8, "width": 5.0, "height": 3.3, "font_size": 12, "font_color": "575757"},

