      {"op": "add_text", "slide_index": 9, "text": "Multi-jurisdiction regulatory\nPre-built compliance modules for OJK (Indonesia), SBV (Vietnam), and BOT (Thailand) regulatory frameworks.\n\nAutomated tax & reporting\nLocal tax calculation engines for VAT, withholding, and e-invoicing mandates. Real-time filing to revenue authorities.\n\nEnterprise-grade security\nSOC 2 Type II, ISO 27001, and local certifications (SNI for Indonesia, PDPA for Thailand). Zero-trust architecture.", "left": 6.7, "top": 2.8, "width": 5.0, "height": 3.3, "font_size": 12, "font_color": "575757"},

